# PartyPeople
 
PartyPeople is a simple API allowing consumers to view information relating to current 
political information. Users can get a list of current elections, candidates in those
elections and details about each candidate, information about political parties and
candidates associated with those parties, and political information about the States
in the US.
 
# Group Candidates
 
## Candidate Collection [/candidates]
  
### List All Candidates [GET /candidates]
Retrieve a list of all the candidates and their data in PartyPeople's database.

+ Response 200 (application/json)
  
        [
            {
                "id": "239394",
                "name": "Ted Cruz",
                "dob": "1970-12-22",
                "current_job": "United States Senator for Texas",
                "party_affiliation": "2",
