### View Candidate Details [GET /candidates/{candidate_id}]
Retrieve the data related to a candidate, using the candidate's unique id.

Returns an object containing a candidate's id, name, date of birth, their current
job, their party affliation, the elections that candidate is currently running in,
their poll numbers, their contact information, and an image url.

+ Parameters
    + candidate_id (number, required) - the unique id of the candidate as an integer
  
+ Response 200 (application/json)
 
        {
            "id": "239394",
            "name": "Ted Cruz",
            "dob": "1970-12-22",
            "current_job": "United States Senator for Texas",
            "party_affiliation": "2",
            "current_elections": [
                "2016 Presidential Election - Republican Nomination",
            ],
            "poll_numbers": "23% favorable",
            "contact_info": {
                "Email": "www.cruz.senate.gov/contact.cfm",
                "Website": "http://www.tedcruz.org/home/",
                "Twitter": "http://twitter.com/SenTedCruz",
                "Facebook": "https://www.facebook.com/tedcruzpage",
                "Phone": "202-224-5922"
            },
            "_links": {
                "thumbnail": {
                    "href": "https://www.tedcruz.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Portrait.jpg"
                }
            }
        }
         
+ Response 404 (text/plain)
        
        Sorry, we do not have information for a candidate with that id.
         
+ Response 410 (text/plain)
        
        The candidate you are searching for not longer exists in our records.
         

