### View Election Details [GET /elections/{election_id}]
Retrieve the data related to an election, using the election's unique id.

Returns an object containing an elections's id, name, date of occurance, the election type
(local, state, or federal), a list of ids of states in which this election is held, a list
of ids of the candidates running in this election, and a link to an image relating to the
election.

+ Parameters
    + election_id (number, required) - the unique id of the election as an integer
  
